sectiondef.header: Methods for reading MEI score-based elements
Methods for reading MEI containers (measures, staff, etc) scoreDef and related.

description.para: For each container (page, system, measure, staff and layer) there is one method for reading the element and one method for reading its children.

The method for reading the children can also be called when reading EditorialElement objects (<lem> or <rdg> for example. The filter object is optional and can be set for filtering the allowed children (see MEIInput::IsAllowed)
